snippet.title: I See Red - Official Teaser Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1594460/I_See_Red/

A frantic twin stick shooter roguelite where you play as a man in search of vengeance. You are so angry and focused on achieving your revenge that you only see the things that you care about the most in RED.



#ISeeRed #WhiteboardGames #roguelike
